{"tid":1690416,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉自品蔥]如何用好黑警濫暴","createTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T10:29:03.000Z","uid":300892,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"463d63e6ad57b971572ab42d4b1270af648f31eb","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"以下只是建議，希望可以被連登手足注意到。<br />\n首先希望所有香港示威者提升大局觀和對中共的客觀認知，中共無疑是一個Great Power，想謀求&ldquo;速勝&rdquo;是不現實的。但中共也有軟肋，最大的軟肋就是中美貿易戰。這個結論從中共對美國的諸多行為之反應，很容易得出，主要有以下幾點：<br />\n在2019年Q3中國GDP增速已經低至6.0%，可以說中共比Donald Trump更有意願達成trade agreement。<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》，外交部對此大肆評論了一番，說明中共其實不care所謂的法案，確實也沒什麼大用。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因此不可以迷信所謂的&ldquo;法案&rdquo;可以帶來多大的作用，刁帝和Donald Trump都是實用主義者。</span></span><br />\n中共真正害怕的是Trade agreement和香港問題掛勾，外交部對於中美貿易x香港的評論少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n目前中美已經達成了一個初步框架性共識（20191026），<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3034670/us-and-china-close-finalising-parts-phase-one-trade-deal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3034670%2Fus-and-china-close-finalising-parts-phase-one-trade-deal&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=c66c1817\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3034670/us-and-china-close-finalising-parts-phase-one-trade-deal</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普警告中國：暴力鎮壓香港示威活動將威脅貿易協議（20190819）<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/特朗普警告中國：不要暴力鎮壓香港示威活動-121566177014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-121566177014&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=38e02db5\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/特朗普警告中國：不要暴力鎮壓香港示威活動-121566177014</a><br />\n<br />\n所以在文宣中，最應該做的就是打破國際社會的思維陷阱，即不出解放軍就不是暴力鎮壓。一定要將黑警濫暴同八九六四聯繫起來，2019的香港黑警就是1989的戒嚴部隊，甚至有過之無不及。Donald Trump和Pence等眾多美國高官，曾多次警告中共，不可以重演六四事件。不妨將1989和2019比對一下，目前黑警的暴力程度，其實已經遠超六四清場前戒嚴部隊的所作所為，這還是在香港尚未戒嚴的情況下。<br />\n<br />\n六四清場-清場前衝突<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/六四清场#清场前冲突\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%B8%85%E5%9C%BA%23%E6%B8%85%E5%9C%BA%E5%89%8D%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=7a7f38ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/六四清场#清场前冲突</a><br />\n<br />\n建議文宣團隊一定要用好黑警濫用暴力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讓國際社會相信，目前的黑警已經黑過六四屠城的戒嚴部隊，並且要與中美貿易戰掛勾</span></span>，或許能有意想不到的奇效。"},{"pid":"2f1554fc52f791425a2679ece3bb058cd2d9dbd4","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7b1bd250c45d63590cab35e6f2b75a7124c1cfe9","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"02aac093f55455fb737c21c7755bf857289fab38","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0dcf70e7c6709d4102ae8f221163b52cc10d4d88","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5fdb7afedc97836ee55a06c48f6b3b46e135aa5a","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b62f7fca01e309685744611ba7cc1d25307c0dc2","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"20465f1c3c1571c249331536b8355fb0a1567497","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"28b021ab309c0e62c4724aac70d62c747754607a","tid":1690416,"uid":300892,"